Comment: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:43.85,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFOT-Lyra Std DB\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}同行之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:08.13,screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs100\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(960,700)}寻求改变的少年
Comment: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord1\fs120\fsp15\fnFZFW-ZHENZTJF-L\c&H020103&\3c&H00013A&\pos(962.667,769.333)}怪物兄弟
